-- Li Ka-shing, Hutchison, Cheung Kong Donate $64 Million to Hong Kong Fund
-- B y   J o s h u a   F e l l m a n
-- 2010-10-14T20:06:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-14/li-ka-shing-hutchison-cheung-kong-donate-64-million-to-hong-kong-fund.html
The Li Ka Shing Foundation and the
 Cheung Kong  (Holdings) Ltd./ Hutchison Whampoa Ltd . group have
pledged HK$500 million ($64 million) to Hong Kong’s government-
lend Community Care Fund, the foundation said.  Li’s charitable body will contribute HK$250 million, with
his two main listed companies contributing an equal amount,
according to a statement posted on the company’s website
yesterday.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Fellman at 
 jfellman@bloomberg.net  